<inglise>9) section 8 is amended by adding subsection (3) worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(3) Registriandmete t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine toimub automatiseeritud andmet&ouml;&ouml;tluse teel vastavalt registripidaja poolt kehtestatud andmet&ouml;&ouml;tluse reeglitele (edaspidi andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlusreeglid). </eesti>
<inglise>"(3) Register information shall be processed by means of automatic data processing according to the rules for data processing established by the registrar (hereinafter data processing rules). </inglise>
<eesti>Andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlusreeglite kehtestamise ja muutmise kord s&auml;testatakse registripidamise korras." </eesti>
