<eesti>10) paragrahvi 10 l&otilde;ike 2 punktid 2 ja 3 muudetakse ning s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>10) clauses 10 (2) 2) and 3) are amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"2) asutatud &auml;ri&uuml;hingu aktsiate v&otilde;i osade registreerimisel &auml;ri&uuml;hingu &auml;riregistri kaardi t&otilde;estatud &auml;rakiri v&otilde;i t&otilde;estatud registri v&auml;ljav&otilde;te v&otilde;i registreerimistunnistuse notariaalselt t&otilde;estatud &auml;rakiri, asutamisel oleva &auml;ri&uuml;hingu aktsiate v&otilde;i osade registreerimisel asutamisotsuse v&otilde;i asutamislepingu notariaalselt t&otilde;estatud &auml;rakiri. </eesti>
<inglise>"2) in the case of registration of shares of an existing company, a certified transcript of the commercial registry card of the company or a certified extract from the register or a notarised transcript of the registration certificate, and in the case of registration of shares of a company under formation, a notarised transcript of the foundation resolution or memorandum of association. </inglise>
<eesti>Eelnimetatud dokumentidele lisab taotluse esitaja oma volitusi t&otilde;endavad dokumendid; </eesti>
<inglise>The applicant shall append documents certifying the authority thereof to the above-mentioned documents; </inglise>
<eesti>3) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite avaliku pakkumise prospekti (edaspidi prospekt) registreerimisel Finantsinspektsiooni poolt antud registreerimisnumbri olemasolu t&otilde;endav dokument ja prospekt;"; </eesti>
<inglise>3) upon registration of a prospectus of a public offer of securities (hereinafter prospectus), a document proving the existence of a registration number granted by the Financial Supervision Authority, and the prospectus;"; </inglise>
<eesti>11) paragrahvi 11 l&otilde;ige 2 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>11) subsection 11 (2) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(2) Kui enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist asutatud aktsiaseltsi aktsiate registreerimisel puudub aktsiaseltsi aktsion&auml;ri nimel registris avatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto, v&otilde;ib registripidaja emitendi taotluse alusel ja emitendi kulul avada aktsion&auml;rile registris ajutise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto." </eesti>
<inglise>"(2) If, upon registration of the shares of a public limited company founded prior to the entry into force of this Act, the shareholder of the company does not have a securities account opened in the register, the registrar may open a temporary securities account in the register for the shareholder on the basis of an application from the issuer and at the expense of the issuer." </inglise>
